    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速且具挑战性的街机游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闪避，传送，前进。在这款游戏中，快速通过各类迷宫，挑战自己。精准的操控和极致的速度将是会您的破局之法。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/ebb8f9bb749518be44c3977d4469c9a0.poster.avif?t=1752740883\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/ebb8f9bb749518be44c3977d4469c9a0.webm?t=1752740883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/ebb8f9bb749518be44c3977d4469c9a0.mp4?t=1752740883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地狱般的难度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/d51eaf94a8e17256bb25be1d76237d7a.poster.avif?t=1752740883\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/d51eaf94a8e17256bb25be1d76237d7a.webm?t=1752740883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/d51eaf94a8e17256bb25be1d76237d7a.mp4?t=1752740883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPEEDRUNNER，这里将是您的舞台</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与自己和其他玩家竞争。每个关卡都有自己的排行榜。您能成为最棒的吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/a4418f42d1b4d3b6bf0167974b76a65f.poster.avif?t=1752740883\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/a4418f42d1b4d3b6bf0167974b76a65f.webm?t=1752740883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204230/extras/a4418f42d1b4d3b6bf0167974b76a65f.mp4?t=1752740883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 超过50个精心设计的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 逐步增加的难度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 每个关卡和模式都有排行榜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 随机元素和方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Roguelite/无限游戏模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 提高每个关卡的通关时间，与其他玩家竞争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 复古未来风美术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 优秀的互动反馈，带来完美的操控感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 根据难度变化的电子音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 速度，追求极致的速度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 我们提到过这款游戏是用满满的爱，精心制作的吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 极具乐趣。</p>",
